50|$|<b>Johannite</b> {{was first}} {{described}} in 1830 by Wilhelm Karl Ritter von Haidinger. It {{was named for}} Archduke John of Austria (1782-1859), {{the founder of the}} Landesmuseum Joanneum (Styria, Austria).|$|E
